'''Magna bolas''' consisted of three heavy, metallic balls attached by a thin wire. They were twirled and thrown at a target, and if aimed correctly, their natural rotation entangled the target in the wire. The metal balls were then activated, producing a strong magnetic attraction which made the bolas nearly impossible to escape.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

